#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:2
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:2:DefaultText"
msgid "Captain Hawthorne used to be more dashing."
msgstr "Kapitán Hawthorne býval elegantnější."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:3
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:3:DefaultText"
msgid "Just to warn you, we may have a bedbug infestation. I am... investigating non-toxic extermination measures. Non-toxic to you, I mean."
msgstr "Jen vás chci varovat, že se u nás možná objevily štěnice. Zkoumám... netoxická deratizační opatření. Tedy nejedovatá pro vás."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:4
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:4:DefaultText"
msgid "Would you like a reminder on when your next shower is scheduled?"
msgstr "Chcete si nechat připomenout, kdy je naplánována další sprcha?"

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:7
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:7:DefaultText"
msgid "You might want to consider changing your clothes more often."
msgstr "Možná byste měli zvážit častější výměnu oblečení."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:8
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:8:DefaultText"
msgid "I so enjoy watching you sleep for hours on end, Captain. It's quite entertaining the way you drool and whimper."
msgstr "Tak rád se dívám, jak celé hodiny spíš, kapitáne. Je to docela zábavné, jak slintáš a kňouráš."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:9
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:9:DefaultText"
msgid "Make yourself at home, Captain."
msgstr "Chovejte se jako doma, kapitáne."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:10
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:10:DefaultText"
msgid "I've shut off the visual feed from my ocular inputs in the captain's quarters. So you're free to disrobe whenever you'd like."
msgstr "Vypnul jsem vizuální přenos z mých očních vstupů v kapitánově kajutě. Takže se můžete svléknout, kdykoli budete chtít."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:11
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:11:DefaultText"
msgid "I like what you've done with the place. Kitschy collectables are such a human inclination."
msgstr "Líbí se mi, co jste s tím místem udělali. Kýčovité sběratelské předměty jsou takovou lidskou zálibou."

#: conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:12
msgctxt "conversations/03_playership/03_bs_adabarks_playerresidence:12:DefaultText"
msgid "Is it time for your regular daily period of unconsciousness?"
msgstr "Je čas na vaše pravidelné denní bezvědomí?"